name: Celebrate
note: Any Pokémon that gets this move is an event Pokémon from 2013: Pikachu, Eevee, and all the eeveelutions.
summary: When the user uses this move, it disappears and a present will show the Pokémon that used this move inside. It then reads,
viability: While there is obviously no use, it's still fun to celebrate! Do it all you want.
